---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="Terms and Conditions | Kalm Moments" description="Terms and Conditions for Kalm Moments Sleep Salon and Massage.">
  <Header />
  <main class="legal-page">
    <article>
      <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p class="effective">Effective Date: 18 December 2024</p>
      
      <h2>01. General Information</h2>
      <p>Kalm Moments ("we," "our," or "us") provides massage, beauty, and wellness services at our salon located in Thailand. Our website allows you to view services, make bookings, and access other information. By using our website or services, you accept and agree to abide by these Terms.</p>

      <h2>02. Booking and Payment</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Booking:</strong> To book a service, you may use our online booking system, contact us directly via phone or email, or visit our salon in person. All bookings are subject to availability.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment:</strong> Payment for services is due at the time of booking or upon completion of the service, depending on the payment method chosen. We accept payments via credit/debit cards, online payment systems, and cash.</li>
        <li><strong>Cancellations and Refunds:</strong> If you need to cancel or reschedule your appointment, please provide at least 24 hours notice. Cancellations made with less notice may be subject to a cancellation fee. Refunds will be provided at our discretion in the event of booking issues, but we reserve the right to refuse refunds under certain circumstances.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>03. Health and Safety</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Health Conditions:</strong> You are responsible for informing us of any medical conditions or allergies that may affect your treatment. Our therapists may refuse service if they believe it may harm your health or well-being.</li>
        <li><strong>Pregnancy and Special Conditions:</strong> If you are pregnant or have any specific health concerns, please consult with your doctor before booking a service. Some treatments may not be suitable for pregnant individuals or those with certain medical conditions.</li>
        <li><strong>Age Restrictions:</strong> Certain treatments or services may have age restrictions, which will be communicated to you upon booking.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>04. Privacy and Personal Data</h2>
      <p>Your use of our website and services is governed by our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>, which outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information. By using our website and services, you consent to the practices described in the Privacy Policy.</p>

      <h2>05. Changes to Terms and Conditions</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to update or modify these Terms at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page with the updated effective date. We recommend that you periodically review these Terms to stay informed about any changes.</p>

      <h2>06. Termination</h2>
      <p>We may suspend or terminate your access to our website or services at our discretion if you violate these Terms or engage in any activity that is harmful to us or our clients. Upon termination, all provisions of these Terms that should survive (such as indemnification and limitations of liability) will remain in effect.</p>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page { padding-top: 100px; padding-bottom: 4rem; }
  .legal-page article {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .legal-page h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-earth);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .effective { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .legal-page h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.25rem; margin: 2rem 0 1rem; }
  .legal-page p, .legal-page li { color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .legal-page ul { margin-left: 1.5rem; }
  .legal-page a { color: var(--color-stone); }
</style>
